winning_structure.name: UBX-NAV-SBAS
winning_structure.description: This message outputs the status of the SBAS sub system.

fields.name: iTOW
fields.description: GPS time of week of the navigation epoch. See the description of iTOW for details.

fields.name: geo
fields.description: PRN Number of the GEO where correction and integrity data is used from

fields.name: mode
fields.description: SBAS Mode (0: Disabled, 1: Enabled integrity, 3: Enabled test mode)

fields.name: sys
fields.description: SBAS System (WAAS/EGNOS/...) (-1: Unknown, 0: WAAS, 1: EGNOS, 2: MSAS, 3: GAGAN, 16: GPS)

bits.name: Ranging
bits.description: GEO may be used as ranging source

bits.name: Bad
bits.description: Problem with signal or broadcast data indicated

bits.name: integrityUsed
bits.description: SBAS integrity used (0: Unknown, 1: Integrity information is not available or SBAS integrity is not enabled, 2: Receiver uses only GPS satellites for which integrity information is available)
